### Pause membership
POST http://localhost:8081/memberships/{{membershipId}}/pause

### Reactivate membership
POST http://localhost:8081/memberships/{{membershipId}}/reactivate

### Suspend membership
POST http://localhost:8081/memberships/{{membershipId}}/suspend
